text.tspan: GDP per head vs. share of industry in employment, 1800 to
The vertical axis shows historical estimates of the share of industry in employment. The horizontal axis shows GDP per head after
adjusting for inflation and price differences across countries (figures are in 2011 international-$).
Data source: OWID based on Herrendorf et al. (2014) and GGDC-10 (2015); Maddison Project Database 2020 (Bolt and van Zanden, 2020)
